Text: Autobytelcom Customer Satisfaction SurveyAutobytelcom Customer Satisfaction Survey TO Kevin Hyatt EMAIL CUSTOMER FROM SUBJECT Autobytelcom Customer Satisfaction Survey Dear Kevin Your satisfaction is important to us so weve developed a survey to evaluate and improve our program By answering our Customer Satisfaction Survey you will help us improve the Autobytelcom online shopping experience Click here to begin the survey surveyindexcfmprnum Customer surveys are a powerful tool we use to evaluate and improve our program By answering our Customer Satisfaction Survey you will help us improve the Autobytelcom online shopping experience Your confirmation number is This request was for a Dodge Ram and was sent to Goodson Dodge Some webbased email readers will not properly load this page if you click on the above link If you experience errors please copy the link and paste it into your browsers address bar Thank you for using Autobytelcom Sincerely Jeffrey Schwartz President Chief Executive Officer Autobytelcom
